info.author: Lars Heuer
info.description:
Package which supports deserialization of the XML Topic Maps (XTM) syntax.

This package can be used to add XTM 1.0 and XTM 2.0 readers to the `tm
<http://pypi.python.org/pypi/tm>`_ package.
info.keywords: Topic Maps, Semantic Web, XTM, XML Topic Maps
info.name: tm.mio.reader.xtm
info.summary: XML Topic Maps (XTM) reader for the Topic Maps package
